text: Oksanna Pizlova (; born 14 November 2000) is an Armenian footballer who plays as a forward for Gyumri and the Armenia women's national team. ==International career== Pizlova capped for Armenia at senior level in a 0–1 friendly loss to Lithuania on 4 March 2020. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Armenian women's footballers Category:Armenia women's international footballers
